Cats are known for their curious nature and love for exploring new objects around the house. However, there are some things that can leave them feeling fearful and intimidated. One such object is the foot scrubber, which has proven to be a source of intrigue and trepidation for many feline companions.

@hanneknygaard, a cat owner based in Norway, recently shared a video of her two cats' reaction to the foot scrubber on 24th April, 2023. In the video, the cats can be seen looking at the scrubber with keen interest, yet also a hint of fear. One of the cats tentatively touches it with its paw, only to quickly run away when the scrubber starts to move.

The other cat, however, stands there curiously watching its mate scampering away, seemingly unafraid. This highlights the differing personalities of cats and how they can react differently to the same object.
